Notes:

1. Make sure the cover design is professionally done so it does not "look" self published  
2. Make sure the editing is impeccable and done by a professional  
3. If she has not taken a book through the publishing process herself before, consider hiring a publishing consultant to do manage the work, the $10 to $100 per hour jobs, so she can stay focused on her 20% best & highest use  
4. Do not publish the book using CreateSpace. Consider instead Lightening Source or IngramSpark for better credibility and distribution.
